    public class PublisherServiceConnector
extends fr.sorbonne_u.components.connectors.AbstractConnector
implements PublisherService.Required
    The PublisherServiceConnector class connects between the PubSub in-bound port and the Publisher out-bound port, the connection between the two ports get established just after the Publisher instantiation.
